*DB:* Well, I appreciate that, thank you. I think about more and more, in o=
ne sense it almost feels exactly like it did 18 years ago, just because we=
=E2=80=99re scrappy, we=E2=80=99re always trying to build stuff, we=E2=80=
=99re looking at the next big step to get to. I think the new thing is more=
 and more a sense of responsibility and a profound sense of the magnitude o=
f what we=E2=80=99re creating and how it impacts people. It=E2=80=99s a lit=
tle bit, as we=E2=80=99ve gotten to where we are, we more and more start th=
inking about the company as a generational company with a big interaction w=
ith society. So I think that=E2=80=99s more of what I=E2=80=99ve started th=
inking about lately.

